#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3820
msgid ""
"Plays on every connected speaker at the same time — wired outputs are "
"delayed to stay in step with Bluetooth."
msgstr ""
"Reproduce en todos los altavoces conectados a la vez — las salidas con cable"
" se retrasan para mantenerse al compás del Bluetooth."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3836
#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3843
msgid "Sync fine-tune"
msgstr "Ajuste fino de sincronía"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3877
msgid ""
"If the Bluetooth speaker still trails the wired ones, raise this until they "
"play together."
msgstr ""
"Si el altavoz Bluetooth aún va detrás de los cableados, sube esto hasta que "
"suenen juntos."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3889
msgid "Sync delay in milliseconds"
msgstr "Retardo de sincronización en milisegundos"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3911
msgid ""
"Type an exact delay in milliseconds — the slider moves in steps of ten."
msgstr ""
"Escribe un retardo exacto en milisegundos — el deslizador se mueve en pasos "
"de diez."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3915
msgid "ms"
msgstr "ms"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3929
msgid "Calibrate with the microphone"
msgstr "Calibrar con el micrófono"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3934
msgid ""
"Plays a few loud clicks through each speaker and measures with the "
"microphone how far the Bluetooth speaker trails — the delay is set "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Reproduce unos clics fuertes por cada altavoz y mide con el micrófono cuánto"
" se retrasa el altavoz Bluetooth — el retardo se ajusta automáticamente."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3949
msgid "Keep sync tuned automatically"
msgstr "Mantener la sincronización ajustada automáticamente"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3952
msgid ""
"Listens to the playing audio with the microphone every few minutes and re-"
"checks the sync when the speakers drift apart. Audio is processed on this "
"computer only — never stored, never sent anywhere."
msgstr ""
"Escucha el audio en reproducción con el micrófono cada pocos minutos y "
"vuelve a comprobar la sincronización cuando los altavoces se desvían. El "
"audio se procesa solo en este equipo: nunca se guarda ni se envía a ninguna "
"parte."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3989
msgid ""
"%1 is remembered for the sync — connect it and it rejoins automatically."
msgstr ""
"%1 está recordado para la sincronización: conéctelo y se reincorporará "
"automáticamente."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4012
msgid "Round 1 of 2 — clicks through every speaker…"
msgstr "Ronda 1 de 2 — clics por cada altavoz…"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4013
msgid "Round 2 of 2 — quiet, checking the result…"
msgstr "Ronda 2 de 2 — silencio, comprobando el resultado…"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4051
msgid "%1 plays in the group"
msgstr "%1 suena en el grupo"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4064
msgid ""
"Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without "
"disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr ""
"Si este altavoz suena en el grupo — desmárcalo para dejarlo fuera sin "
"desconectarlo. Se recuerda para el dispositivo."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4073
msgid "%1 (nothing plugged in)"
msgstr "%1 (nada conectado)"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4087
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "Balance de %1"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4096
msgid ""
"This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move "
"and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the"
" per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched "
"layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr ""
"La parte de este altavoz en el volumen: el balance sigue cada movimiento del"
" control maestro y se recuerda para el dispositivo. Solo afecta a lo que "
"reproduce este widget; el volumen por dispositivo en los ajustes de sonido "
"del sistema es una capa aparte e intacta — por eso esos números difieren de "
"estos deslizadores."

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4113
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4114
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4115
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
msgid "M"
msgstr "M"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4116
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays plain stereo"
msgid "ST"
msgstr "ST"

#: package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:4121
msgid ""
"Which channels this speaker plays: stereo, left only, right only, or a mono "
"mix of both. Set one speaker to L and another to R for a true stereo pair — "
"remembered for the device."
msgstr ""
"Qué canales reproduce este altavoz: estéreo, solo izquierdo, solo derecho o "
"una mezcla mono de ambos. Pon un altavoz en L y otro en R para un verdadero "
"par estéreo — se recuerda para el dispositivo."

